default academic medicine 
defaultand dentistry staffing levels shows that
default, as 
defaultfor 
defaultother STEM subjects, there continues to be a small proportion of women 
defaultProfessors (16%), particularly when compared with Senior Lecturer/Readers (32% medicine, 39% dentistry) and Lecturers (44%). Yet HESA data show that 54% of medical students and 59% of dental students are women. Progression from Lecturer grade is a key chal
defaultlenge for female academics.
